data.description: Welcome to your cozy new home! Only a short drive from Highway I-10, this home is close to all of San Antonio's hot spots. The enclosed front porch is a nice touch that adds extra living space and provides a cozy spot for enjoying the outdoors and a morning cup of coffee. The interior of the home boasts a lovely four bedrooms and living room offering plenty of space for a family or for entertaining guests. The backyard offers ample space to use as desired. Turn this blank canvas into your own personal outdoor oasis. Being within walking distance to MLK Middle School and MLK Park is a great bonus, making this home perfect for families with children. Schedule your private tour today!
